Task ID: \h(《Galcian》)Well, Vyse…\e
\h(《Galcian》)It looks like we meet again.\e
\h(《Vyse》)Galcian!\e

\h(《Galcian》)Heh… Not only once, but twice, you escaped from
the Grand Fortress. Very impressive.\e

\h(《Galcian》)However… do not think you will escape 
a third time.\e

\h(《Enrique》)Galcian…
What is Valua planning to do by building
a place like this?\e

\h(《Galcian》)If it isn't the Little Prince…
Whatever Valua does, Your Highness, is no longer
any of your concern, if I'm not mistaken.\e

\h(《Galcian》)You were the one who threw away your
responsibilities and sided with these… pirates.\e

\h(《Enrique》)I did not throw away my responsibilities! 
I am working to rebuild the Empire!\e

\h(《Galcian》)Heh heh heh… It matters not to me.
I have no interest in Valua anymore.\e
\h(《Galcian》)I shall dispose of you here, once and for all.\e
\h(《Enrique》)…\e

\h(《Vyse》)This is great…

\h(《Aika》)Vyse!

\h(《Gregorio》)It has been a while, Prince Enrique.\e
\h(《Enrique》)Gregorio?!!\e

\h(《Enrique》)How ironic… that fate has lead us both here to
pit sword against sword with each other.\e

\h(《Gregorio》)Do not worry.
I am not here to fight you.\e
\h(《Enrique》)What? What are you doing?!\e

\h(《Galcian》)Gregorio…
You understand the consequences of your
actions…\e

\h(《Gregorio》)Lord Galcian…
It appears that YOU do not understand the
consequences of YOUR actions.\e

\h(《Gregorio》)You wish to revive the ancient horrors and use
them to make the world yours…\e

\h(《Gregorio》)I cannot sit back and watch you destroy the
world!\e
\h(《Enrique》)What are you doing?\e

\h(《Gregorio》)Prince… you spoke the truth when we last met 
at Esparanza. The Empire has chosen 
the wrong path.\e

\h(《Gregorio》)You and Vyse are the only ones that can stop the
Armada.\e

\h(《Gregorio》)Prince Enrique… 
Let my last act be in your honor.\e
\h(《Enrique》)Why?\e

\h(《Gregorio》)I will hold him off.
Escape while you can.\e

\h(《Enrique》)What are you saying?!
We will fight with you!\e

\h(《Gregorio》)You must not take Galcian lightly! 
He is more powerful than you can imagine.\e

\h(《Gregorio》)And this is a military base of the Armada… 
If you don't escape soon, we will all be
surrounded.\e
\h(《Gregorio》)If you die here… the world will be doomed.\e

\h(《Gregorio》)Go… our last hopes lie with you… 
Young Prince.\e

\h(《Gregorio》)I earned the nickname Iron Wall Admiral.
I won't let him past me.\e

\h(《Gregorio》)And, I will be able to die defending you.
I cannot ask for a higher honor.\e
\h(《Enrique》)Wait! Don't do this!!!\e

\h(《Gregorio》)Young Prince… Captain Vyse…
Please… You must stop Galcian… 
You are our last hope…\e
\h(《Gregorio》)Farewell!\e
\h(《Enrique》)NOOO!!!\e

\h(《Galcian》)Gregorio…
Have you made your peace?\e

\h(《Gregorio》)I am ready to die, Lord Galcian, but I shall die
defending my people against a tyrant.\e

\h(《Vyse》)Hm?
I can hear someone talking…\e

\h(《Valuan Soldier》)Moon Energy System operating within normal
parameters. Power supply to the entire base

\h(《Valuan Soldier》)Okay, the inspection for this area is done.
Let's go to the next one.\e

for the base's power.)\c

\h(《Vyse》)(I think that's the control area

\h(《Vyse》)It's a fan. It's probably for ventilation.
I don't think I should get too close…\e

\h(《Vyse》)But, it looks like there's a passageway behind

\h(《Vyse》)Whoa, now that's scary…

\h(《Valuan Soldier》)So, these are the schematics that Lord De Loco

\h(《Valuan Soldier》)That's what I hear. But it's not like I

\h(《Vyse》)We can't let Gregorio's sacrifice be in vain!

\h(《Valuan Soldier》)I still don't get why they would build a base

Lord Galcian is building a new

\h(《Valuan Soldier》)Did you know that Lord Galcian has never been

\h(《Valuan Soldier》)You… you're Vyse!?
What are you doing here!?\c
